mappingId	mapping-1131651604
target		<http://example.com/best_paper_awards_committ/{ID}> a sigkddstructured:Best_Paper_Awards_Committee ; sigkddstructured:isCommitteeOf <http://example.com/conference/{hasCommittee_Inv}> , <http://example.com/conference/{isCommitteeOf}> ; sigkddstructured:award <http://example.com/best_research_paper_award/{award}> . 
